\\\\ Stack operations

\\\\ @ = DUP (duplicate top)
!5 @ + |    \\\\ 10 (5 + dup of 5)

\\\\ # = SWAP (swap top two)
!1 !2 # | |  \\\\ prints 1 then 2 (swapped)

\\\\ $ = DROP (discard top)
!1 !2 !3 $ | |  \\\\ prints 2 then 1

\\\\ 0-99 = push variable value
\\\\ : = store to variable (pop val, pop addr, store)
!42 !0 :    \\\\ store 42 in var 0
0 |         \\\\ print var 0 (42)
